data.description: This home has an assumable VA 2.75% interest rate loan. And you do not have to be a Veteran to assume the loan! Perfect for entertaining, this beautiful 7 bedroom home with a game room and two living areas is located in a gated community minutes from I-20 sitting on just under a quarter of an acre with a pool and covered pergola in Kennedale ISD! This home has a split floorplan with the primary bedroom and a second bedroom down and a cute oversized gas fireplace. This home gets great natural light, has a 3 car garage, and a tankless water heater. Book your tour today!
